.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/a8ec97747226e4e2dd1a4ce649828bc7.webp?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your run with a standard-issue rifle and loot for powerful attachments like explosive charms, poison gun barrels, tactical scopes, silencers, and more. If you fall to enemy fire, survive long enough to retrieve your fallen soul or lose your run progress to permadeath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.poster.avif?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.webm?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1025ec4f6b779d6d527152291ac6cbb3.mp4?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/fddf5ef2f5c8b1f9a25f6c42a44d4f11.webp?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cleanse the souls of the fallen to climb the ranks of The Light Brigade and spend rank points to upgrade your weapon, passive abilities, and spells. Unlock new player classes and gain access to new weapons, loadouts and play styles, adding even more variety to your runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/5dad6cf485f7e6a3d07d0e8e582854b3.webp?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot treasure chests and enemies during your run to collect an array of magical tarot cards, each with unique powers, buff/debuffs and passive abilities. Acquire stronger versions of these cards to create devastating stacking effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/5c5a7f135ca54ac0ac3c811933f67b11.avif?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/58009c490ae5633ea1df320e1ac2e2b7.poster.avif?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/58009c490ae5633ea1df320e1ac2e2b7.webm?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/58009c490ae5633ea1df320e1ac2e2b7.mp4?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/72a5adf32410d6454932b7bcdbb7fae8.webp?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitely procedurally-generated battlegrounds make each run completely unique, forcing you to traverse carefully through ever-changing hostile environments. Enemy soldiers lurk around every corner, so position and strategy is crucial for survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.poster.avif?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.webm?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/1ca9c907a8f180e64e63fcc0c7c954ca.mp4?t=1772479879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/6cc77237006c36ae5367395c346fe981.webp?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What led to the world's downfall? What do the Obsidian Forces want? Uncover these mysteries and bring the world back from the brink of total darkness before it's too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579880/extras/bee4f02928a684ebb74a818105e964a1.avif?t=1772479879\" width=600 height=769 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've been hard at work on <strong>future updates</strong> and are currently in production on a wide variety of post-launch content. Given the modular design of our roguelike system, it is fun & seamless to continuously add more to the game. So expect new content in the form of new biomes/worlds, enemies, guns/weapons, unlockable player classes, attachments, online features, items, as well as general improvements to the user experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you'd like to stay updated on our development, you can follow along by joining our Discord.</p>",
